content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4624.18 - Financial statement to be filed by lessor

State Regulations
A licensed authorized games of chance lessor shall
execute and file a financial statement of rental income on form GC-9, as
prescribed by the commission. The original of the form shall be filed with the
licensing authority and one copy with the commission. Notes
